snippet.title: Project Timi: Sasha's Curse - Official Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description:
Project Timi: Sasha's Curse is a 3D rhythmic puzzle-packed action game mashup. Use the rhythm of the music to activate magic traps, fight nightmare creatures, explore dream worlds, and uncover all the secrets hidden away in Lucity Town. 

Check out the new Project Timi: Sasha's Curse trailer for a look at the game, coming to Nintendo Switch and PC. You can wishlist it now on Steam.
